headline: Generac Announces Fourth Quarter and Full-Year 2025 Earnings Release Date and Conference Call
summary: WAUKESHA, Wis., Jan. 28, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Generac Holdings Inc. ("Generac") (NYSE: GNRC), a leading global designer, manufacturer, and provider of energy technology solutions and other power products, today announced plans to release its fourth quarter and full-year 2025 financial results before the market opens on Wednesday, February 11, 2026.
